author: More Perfect Union
description:
We asked a question that oddly enough doesn't get much attention: How did Jeffrey Epstein get rich in the first place?

The answer is a strange mix of scamming, helping the wealthy dodge taxes, and subprime mortgages.

Epstein is, ultimately, a product of our corrupt system.
title: The Epstein Crimes You Haven’t Heard About, Part 2
